# Production build for the portable kit.
#
# Empty VITE_MCP_URL = same-origin requests. The chat-ui static files are
# served by `gitnexus.exe serve` itself (from `<bin_dir>/web/`) so /api/chat,
# /api/repos and /mcp resolve to the same host:port the page was loaded from.
# No reverse proxy, no CORS dance, no separate dev server.
VITE_MCP_URL=
